<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَلَوْا بِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>صَارُوا بِهِ أَسْيَادَ هَاتِيكَ الأُمَمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَبَصَرْخَةٍ مِنْ بَاكِيَةْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>الأَرْضُ يَكْسُوهَا اللَّهِيبْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَسُيُوفُهُمْ دَوَّى الصَّلِيلُ كَأَنَّهُ الرَّعْدُ الرَّهِيبْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَالأَرْضُ تَرْوِيهَا الدِّمَاءُ الْغَادِرَةْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَالْحَقُّ يَعْلُو دَائِمًا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>لا يَظْلِمُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لا يُظْلَمُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَالْكُفْرُ يَسْقُطُ تَحْتَ أَقْدَامِ الأُبَاةْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>لا يَصْمُدُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>هَلْ يَصْمُدَنْ فِي وَجْهِ قَوْمٍ مَوْتُهُمْ نِعْمَ الْحَيَاةْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فِي جَنَّةِ الْفِرْدَوْسِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>